            "answer_text": "Write a fan letter; most authors have websites (which you can find by googling), and most author websites include some way to contact the author (often through an intermediary, such as the webmaster). Many authors are on Facebook or Twitter, as well. Write a review on Amazon. Even if you don\u2019t have anything to say beyond, \u201cI loved this book!\u201d the mere number of reviews helps make the book more visible to casual browsers. ",
